<abstract><t>This draft describes operational procedures aimed at reducing the amount of traffic lost during planned maintenances of routers or links, involving the shutdown of BGP peering sessions.  It defines a well-known BGP community, called GRACEFUL_SHUTDOWN, to signal the graceful shutdown of paths.</t></abstract>

